comment5.text=\n\ Called\ once\ every\ clock\ tick\ (frequency\ specified\ by\ the\ "interval"\ method)\n\ to\ draw\ the\ next\ animation-frame.\ Typically\ this\ is\ used\ to\ update\ the\ animation's\n\ data\ to\ reflect\ the\ passage\ of\ time\ (e.g.,\ to\ modify\ an\ instance\ variable\ that\ gives\n\ the\ position\ of\ an\ object)\ before\ the\ frame\ is\ drawn.\n\ \n\ @param\ g\ the\ Graphics\ object\ on\ which\ to\ draw\ the\ animation-frame.\n
